    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies for exceptional throttle response. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal power distribution. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a recently serviced dual-VANOS system, addressing critical preventative maintenance items. The suspension retains its factory geometry with MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup, providing the communicative feedback this chassis is legendary for. While the exterior shows light patina typical of a driven classic, the mechanical vitals remain robust and track-ready.",
      "price": 34500.0,
