    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a well-maintained example that offers a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag. The exterior finish presents beautifully, retaining a high-gloss luster, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the passenger door. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the leather seating is supple with only light creasing on the driver's side bolster. Every feature, including the panoramic sunroof, heated seats, and navigation system, is fully operational. Under the hood, the car has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule. Recent maintenance includes a cooling system flush, new ceramic brake pads, and a fresh battery. The tires have ample tread depth, and the suspension remains tight and quiet over bumps. Sale includes a full set of floor mats, two remote fobs, and a documented service history to provide peace of mind for the next owner.",
